{
  "texts": [
    "This necessitates some measure of societal impact of research.",
    "For example, in the UK there has been much emphasis now on \"public engagement\" and, even more so, on \"impact\".",
    "Both of those have obvious advantages as alternative means of evaluating scientific contributions, but they are also beset with problems because they are often difficult to measure or evaluate.",
    "One solution is to consider output that can be easily counted (such as being cited in policy decisions, legal briefs, etc.)",
    "that shows how one's work is impacting the world."
  ]
}